        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Estate Tax Reduction Act of 2003 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) reduce estate tax rates; (2) repeal the phaseout of graduated rates; and (3) increase the unified credit to $2.5 million, with an inflation adjustment.</p>]]></text>
